"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-lifestyle-celeb-news-international-celebs-ariana-grande-and-cynthia-erivo-turn-heads-at-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9538761020834963, \"rank\": 0.04832607085241162, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbLifestyle\\u00bbCeleb News\\u00bbInternational Celebs\\u00bbAriana Grande and Cynthia Erivo turn heads at Paris Olympics  Actresses Ariana Grande and Cynthia Erivo made a remarkable appearance at the Paris 2024 Olympics opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 397, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9538761020834963, \"rank\": 0.04832607085241162, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 238, \"end\": 251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cynthia Erivo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\"}, {\"begin\": 310, \"end\": 323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cynthia Erivo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ariana Grande and Cynthia Erivo have just cast their spell at the Paris 2024 Olympics with a fashion moment straight out of the Land of Oz.\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 399, \"end\": 412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariana Grande\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\"}, {\"begin\": 417, \"end\": 430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cynthia Erivo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The duo made a stunning entrance at the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They embraced their iconic roles from the upcoming film adaptation ofWicked.\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 674, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Grande, known for her ethereal pop hits, dazzled in a bubblegum pink Thom Browne dress, according toCosmopolitan.\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 789, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The outfit was completed with pristine white gloves, creating a look that perfectly channels her character, Glinda the Good Witch.\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 899, \"end\": 905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glinda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Glinda\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glinda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glinda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her ensemble, described as \\\"Glinda meets Breakfast at Tiffany's,\\\" captured theessenceof the beloved witch's whimsical and elegant style.\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 1059, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 951, \"end\": 957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glinda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Glinda\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glinda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glinda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cynthia Erivo, who stars as Elphaba in the film, matched Grande's enchantment with her own striking green gown.\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1061, \"end\": 1074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cynthia Erivo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\"}, {\"begin\": 1089, \"end\": 1096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elphaba\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elphaba\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elphaba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elphaba\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The outfit was paired with a coordinating hat, making it an impeccable nod to Elphaba's iconic wardrobe.\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1278, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1252, \"end\": 1259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elphaba\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elphaba\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elphaba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elphaba\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The green ensemble was not just a tribute but a visual feast.\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1341, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It evoked the character's magical aura.\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair's thematic attire was no mere coincidence.\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Both Grande and Erivo are in the midst of a promotional whirlwind forWicked.\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1512, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Their Olympic appearance only underscores their commitment to the film's promotional campaign.\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1608, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Their growing friendship is also evident, adding a layer of charm to their joint appearances, according toPeople.\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1723, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Erivo praised Grande's talent, saying, \\\"I just need to say that I do not think people realise that she's got the chops.\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1844, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think people realise how brilliant this person's brain and voice and talent is.\\\"\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 1935, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ariana Grande echoed this admiration, remarking, \\\"She's my favourite female voice.\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 2019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1937, \"end\": 1950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariana Grande\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I was watching you sing at the Oscars, I said, 'I hope someday I get to sing with her.'\\\"\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2114, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2057, \"end\": 2063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Academy_Awards\", \"score\": 0.9924722723271846, \"rank\": 0.007584824118838619, \"text\": \"Oscars\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Academy_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Academy_Awards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris 2024 Olympics is not just a stage for athletic achievement but also a showcase of cultural moments.\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2126, \"end\": 2139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ariana Grande and Cynthia Erivo's appearance is a perfect example of how pop culture intersects with global events, according to theHollywood Reporter.\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2378, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2227, \"end\": 2240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariana Grande\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\"}, {\"begin\": 2245, \"end\": 2258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cynthia Erivo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cynthia_Erivo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their outfits not only paid tribute to their roles but also created a buzz that captured the spirit of the occasion.\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2496, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the world watches, the excitement surroundingWickedcontinues to build.\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2571, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Grande and Erivo's stylish nod to their characters has set a high bar for the upcoming film's promotional tour.\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With their chemistry and flair, it's clear that this is only the beginning of a thrilling ride for fans of both the Olympics andWicked.\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For now, the magic of Glinda and Elphaba continues to enchant as Grande and Erivo bring a touch of Broadway sparkle to the heart of Paris.\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2961, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2845, \"end\": 2851,